        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 8.4</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\r\n  <p>Inform the staff about the password policies and procedures.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>The staff should be familiar with the password policies and procedures so that they can comply.</p>\r\n  <h1>How</h1>\r\n  <p>Distribute a copy of the password policy and a memo about the password procedures among the employees and instruct the employees to become familiar with them.</p>"
